{
  "stem": "3848.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, I decided to go back to do-- to my work to Zdolbuniv.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I figured in the morning, the first thing after my job is finished, I will run back to the city and see what happened to my family.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Well, it didn't happen that way, because when I came to work, I was on the station.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In-- after 10 o'clock, about 11 o'clock, they German planes came again and started to bombard that big station that was there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "There were soldiers up there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And there was ammunition on the-- on the station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they tried to knock it out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, while I was there in between all the cars and the locomotives and the planes, I-- I thought, it's not a good idea to stay here.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went out from this station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I ran out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I walked towards the outskirts of Zdolbuniv.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Being that I was very tired and didn't sleep for the last three days coming from Lvov, I walked into one of the houses there-- it was mostly Gentile people lived there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I asked if it's OK for me to lie down and sleep there until the morning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, would you please wake me up in the morning, very early in the morning, so I could get out and run back to work?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There are already some men there sleeping on the floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you want to lie down on the floor, it's OK.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she claims she couldn't wake me up early in the morning because that's how tired I was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I walked out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was already daylight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I ran back towards the station to see what happened over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
